    BOOK NOW > Made in Leicestershire Professional Development Events

    Creative Leicestershire and our Made in Leicestershire consultant Ruth Singer will be hosting a fantastic Made in Leicestershire networking event in September - We would like you to be involved! This is for visual artists and makers in Leicestershire + Rutland, both established or start up.


    It is an excellent opportunity for professional development, mentoring and networking. Places are limited, please book ASAP via the link below.


    _____________________________________________


    Made in Leicestershire Network Day


    24 September at LCB Depot, 31 Rutland St Leicester LE1 1RE

    1.00pm – 4.00PM


    A special event for visual artists and makers from Leicester, Leicestershire and Rutland, designed to help you expand and grow your skills, knowledge and connections within our creative community.


    This whole event, including refreshments, is just £5 for artists and makers from Leicestershire and Rutland.*


    The event will include :


    Professional development talks from well-known artists and makers from outside the county, plus curators and mentors.


    - Launch of our new online directory

    - Launch of our new publication showcasing some of the finest local talent and sharing ideas for growing the network in the future

    - Chance to meet and get to know other artists and makers from the county and build friendship groups which will support your practice in the future

    - 1:1 business advice slots (must be booked in advance)


    Times subject to change, finalised programme will be updated here the week before the event.
